name: {DD} Reverse cowgirl with soles (feet on lap)
description:
This Lora came out unexpected, I tried to fix this Lora, "cure" it from bad quality artifacts, but understood, that soles are too complicated for SD, and create morbid mutants if left in the dataset. So I thought to cleanse my set from images that containt soles.

Then I thought, that this pose is beautifull, and it woul be a shame to lose it completely. And then I gathered some additional images with soles and feet, and here we are.

Well feet are really complicated (try to draw one yourself, to understand that). So expect only 3 out of 10 decent images, or even less - others will be weird.

Tags (shouldn't be necessary)

Soles, from behind

Parameters suggestions

Should work in txtToImg with sides somewhere between 512-768

Weights between 0.5-1

Clip skip - I didn't use it

Pay attention to the sampler model - my standard Karras 2M wasn't good all the time. For realistic I found out that dpm adaptive is better (at leasts for me and for that exact Lora). So use x/y/z to find the best combination of parametrs.

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)
